<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Slop" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Slop,</orth> large loose trowsers: <cit><quote>a German from the waist downward, all --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 3.2.36" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado III, 2, 36</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>my short cloak and my --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 1.2.34" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B I, 2, 34</bibl></cit>. <emph>a French salutation</emph> <cit><quote>to your French s.</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 2.4.47" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. II, 4, 47</bibl></cit>. In <bibl n="shak. lll 4.3.59" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL IV, 3, 59</bibl> O. Edd. <emph>shop,</emph> some M. Edd. <emph>slop.</emph>
